description: 听对话，根据对话的内容，从下面各题所给的选项中选择最佳选项。录音听两遍。

content.contentDesc:
W: Can I help you, sir?

M: I want to buy two kilos of oranges and four kilos of bananas.

W: All right. These oranges and bananas are very fresh. Here you are.

Q: How many kilos of bananas has the man bought?

description: 听对话，根据对话的内容，从下面各题所给的选项中选择最佳选项。录音听两遍。

content.contentDesc:
M: Hello! Are you a new student in this class?

W: Yes. My name is Linda. Nice to meet you.

M: I'm Mike. Nice to meet you, too. We are going to the zoo this Sunday. Would you like to go with us?

W: Sure. I love animals very much.

subContents.content: Where are they going this Sunday? They are going to the _____.

content.content: I think the best place to visit on weekends is the zoo. When you are free, you can go _____ your family. _____ the zoo, there are many _____ like pandas, koalas, dolphins, lions and _____ animals. _____ are the biggest (最大的) animals on land (陆地上). Lions come from _____. They live in the forest (森林). I want to see lions. And I _____ a baby lion was born (出生) there last Friday. Sally wants _____ with me this weekend. But I have _____ homework to do. I must finish (完成) my homework _____. Then we can have a good time there.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是介词辨析。句意：当你有空的时候，你可以和你的家人一起去动物园。in 在……内；with 和……一起；from 来自于；and 和，又，而。

因此，正确答案是B。

此题考查的是词语辨析。句意：在动物园里，有许多种动物，如熊猫、考拉、大象、狮子和其他动物。in 在……内；on 在……上；for 为了；to 到。

因此，正确答案是A。

此题考查的是名词辨析。句意：在动物园里，有许多种动物,如熊猫、考拉、大象、狮子和其他动物。people 人；child 孩子；animal 动物；bird 鸟。

因此，正确答案是C。

此题考查的是不定代词辨析。句意：在动物园里，有许多种动物像熊猫、考拉、大象、狮子和其他动物。another 又一个；the other 另一个；others 其他的,别的；other 其他的，别的。other和others均表示不确指意义,其中other后可以修饰名词,而others后不能再接名词,两者的关系可描述为:others=other+复数名词。由于空后面有名词animals。

因此，正确答案是D。

此题考查的是名词辨析。句意：大象是陆地上最大的动物。elephant 大象；koala 考拉；panda 熊猫；lion 狮子。

因此，正确答案是A。

此题考查的是名词辨析。句意：狮子来自于非洲。Australia 澳大利亚；China 中国；Canada 加拿大；Africa 非洲。

因此，正确答案是D。

此题考查的是动词辨析。句意：而我知道一个幼狮于上周五在那里出生。know 知道，及物动词；listen 听，不及物动词。主语是第一人称。

因此，正确答案是C。

此题考查的是短语固定搭配。句意：Sally这周末想和我一起去动物园。want to do sth. 想要做某事。

因此，正确答案是C。

此题考查的是不定代词的辨析。句意：但是我有许多的推荐要去做。homework是不可数名词，a few和many后面接可数名词；little 一点也没有；lots of 许多。

因此，正确答案是D。

此题考查的是副词。句意：我必须先完成推荐。first 首先，第一；in first 不是固定结构 ；at last 最后；last 最后的。

因此，正确答案是A。

W: I agree with you.

content.contentDesc:
W: Where were you yesterday afternoon, Fred?

M: Do you mean during basketball practice, Mary?

W: Yes. What happened to you?

M: I had to go to the doctor's again. Was Mr. Smith angry? I forgot to tell him I was not going to take part in it.

W: Well, he wasn't very happy about it.

M: How was the practice?

W: Not very good. Everybody seemed tired. And Tom got hurt.

M: Was he hurt badly?

W: No. He hurt his arm a little. He's OK today. And of course, Charles can't play because of his leg.

M: Who played instead of Charles?

W: Ray did. He's not very good.

M: What about Carl? He's fast.

W: Yes, but he's short. Well, you've got to be there this afternoon. Four o'clock as usual.

M: I know. I'll be there then.

subContents.content: What did Fred do yesterday afternoon?

options.option: He went to the doctor.

subContents.content: What time will the basketball practice begin this afternoon?
